<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Arudāladharmmavarttiyagu naṁdhranarēśvaru sarvva <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <unclear>vāriki</unclear>ṁ brabhaviṁcce nāvaya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> dōḥ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śauri vāniki janiyiṁcce guṁḍena manīṣijanapraṇu<unclear>tu</unclear>ṁḍu vānikiṁ jakitakuraṁgalōcanakuṁ jaṁdanagaṁdhiki 
<lb n="3"/>guppamāṁbakunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> dhīruṁḍu gaśyapagōtrōddhāruṁḍu guṁḍimaḍavibhuṁ ḍudāruṁḍu madanākāruṁḍu gava<unclear>liya</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>yannaṁḍu gāravamunaṁ buṭṭi vaṁśakaruṁḍai pērmmini <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1071 gunēṁṭi Uttarāyanasaṁkrāṁti nimi<unclear>tta</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>muna śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalēśvara tribhuvanamalladēva pottappicōḍamahārājula kavaliya Annaya kammanāṁṭi prēṁpalli śrībhā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vanārāyaṇadēvara kakhaṁḍavarttidīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vīniṁ jēkoni Aṁggarika jakkanabōyini koḍku gāma
<lb n="7"/>dana putrānupautrikamu nitya māneṁḍu neyi vō <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> garādhyakṣa koṭṭiyadona <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>naṁdula mahīdharāśīnuṁḍaina śrīkēśavadēvuna kannāṁṭi<unclear>lōṁ</unclear> jaḍi sanna bhāvanārāyaṇunaku dākṣārāma<unclear>pu</unclear>
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ri bhīmanāthadēvaraku dannāḍa haimavatīvallabhunaku nīvanikaṁḍravāḍilō mahanīyyamagu guṁḍimaḍayu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ku
<lb n="10"/>moṭṭavāḍi nanupamamagu tripurāṁtakēśvarunaku nacalabhaktidriḍhamugā nakhaṁḍadīpamulu nilipe [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] <unclear>punyārji</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>ṁḍamātyannaṁ<unclear>ḍu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kuṁṭita<unclear>mā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> managuṁḍayayanna <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> miginaṭṭiṁṭi nidhā<unclear>na</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <note n="66-1">The remaining lines are badly damaged.</note>
</p>

